	  RelaxngPattern.cs,
	  RelaxngReader.cs :
	  Use XmlResolver (or XmlUrlResolver) directly. XmlResolver was
	  incorrectly _used_ before null check. Don't create XmlResolver
	  instance for _every_ pattern object.
